\n\n<p>&#8211; Explore cost-effective alternatives for furniture and materials.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8211; Repurpose existing furniture and accessories wherever possible.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8211; Get quotes from multiple designers to compare prices and services.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8211; Keep track of all expenses and prioritise your spending wisely.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. How much does hiring a budget interior designer in Bangalore cost?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The cost of hiring a budget interior designer in Bangalore can vary depending on factors such as the scope of the project, the designer&#8217;s experience, and your specific requirements. Generally, the fees can range from Rs. 30,000 to Rs. 60,000 for a small project and from Rs. 2,00,000 to Rs. 5,00,000 for a larger project. It is recommended to discuss your budget and project details with the designer to get an accurate estimate.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' 